Subject: [PATCH] jfs: Fix array index bounds check in dbAdjTree
Patch-mainline: v5.10.4
References: openEuler-21.03

stable inclusion
from stable-5.10.4
commit c2032bf94ba4fb15db0c277614338d377fe430d2
